{"tid":532597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七旬清潔工疑誤取印花當膠紙翌早即歸還 萬寧稱值三萬照報警（2)","createTime":"2018-01-18T03:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T10:54:50.000Z","uid":140979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa50f1e6b08de6dd17da4b93615989e57e6887ca","tid":532597,"uid":140979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"左眼幾乎失明的77歲獨居婆婆不欲領綜援，靠每天連當數份兼職外判清潔工糊口。婆婆稱去年在工作了十多年的萬寧荃錦中心分店值勤期間，誤將一卷印花當成膠紙放進褲袋，預備用來固定垃圾袋，後來卻因有大量紙皮需清理，手忙腳亂忘記了原先的工作。婆婆回家後才驚覺誤把印花拿回家，翌日早早在公司門外等待開閘，並將印花放回原位。惟萬寧保安咬定婆婆盜竊並報警處理。萬寧稱，該卷近600個印花價值約三萬元。<br />\n<br />\n婆婆李淑卿（77歲）被控盜竊罪，控罪指她於去年7月21日犯案，意圖永久剝奪屬於萬寧的財產。萬寧計算出的印花價值不菲，608個印花每個價值50元。控方證供主要依賴萬寧保安趙愛虹、案發閉路電視片段及被告警誡下的招認。<br />\n<br />\n不認罪的李婆婆今於庭上自辯，她神情緊張，手不時顫抖，說話有時乏力，裁判官亦提醒辯方大狀盡量讓婆婆慢慢說話，免得遺漏了她的重要證言。<br />\n<br />\n李婆婆透露她於印尼出生，80年代定居香港，早年離婚的現獨居，兒子已逝世，女兒則間中才聯絡。她直言「唔想申請綜援」，因想盡量靠自己，十多年來每天在四間店舖當兼職清潔。涉案的荃灣萬寧，她已經工作了十多年。據了解，她另於兩間萬寧任清潔工，案發後已遭辭退<br />\n<br />\n李婆婆表示左眼幾乎失明，右眼視力模糊，她需戴眼鏡，但有時「戴下除下」，案發時剛好沒戴。案發早上她七點多上班，她在收銀台找不到膠紙座，便在台下找到一卷白色東西。她以為這是膠紙便放入褲袋，以便騰出雙手工作。她指當天有大量紙皮需拆盒，沒理會褲袋的膠紙，她又趕著下班緊接下一份兼職，一直上班接下班，晚上11時多才回家洗澡，發現褲袋有一卷印花<br />\n<br />\n當時已近深夜，她不知所措，翌朝公司未開門，她已在門口等待。店門一開她已將印花放回原位。後來她正要下班時，保安員趙愛虹即攔截她並搜她的袋。趙曾向警方稱在李袋即時搜出一卷印花及10個零散印花，但辯方後來要求取得22日的閉路電視，證實李婆婆將印花放回台上。<br />\n<br />\n李婆婆指該10數個零散印花是她購物時取得的，她根本沒有儲印花的習慣，故取得印花後會隨便放入袋，她直言那些印花她「要嚟都唔知做乜」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方在結案陳詞指，閉路電視拍到李婆婆案發翌朝已歸還印花，根本沒有剝奪任何人的財產，加上有另一間聘用李婆婆的店舖職員出庭證明婆婆勤勞有責任感，希望法庭判李婆婆無罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180117&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57719681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180117%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57719681&d=hZ%2Fq%2Fd2VlDcwjyJMHBVxpgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=130c3675\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180117%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57719681&h=11438ace\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180117&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57719681</a>"},{"pid":"ba39f6646cc816d1770bfa2fa33647f1b94aafd6","tid":532597,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1592fc78d2de4431febfc5b3380498d06a3b5066","tid":532597,"uid":160662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:01:21.000Z","msg":"三大笑點<br />\n個食蕉阿姐同阿婆咁大仇口, 做假口供都要做阿婆<br />\n萬寧為左呢D野去告, 仲要話d印花值三皮野, 關公真係<br />\n差佬見呢D case最多警司警誡下就算, 搞到要上court浪費社會資源"},{"pid":"d5d82db67542cf7a2e2256a11676aea9f5a6c33a","tid":532597,"uid":16970,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:01:36.000Z","msg":"李指左眼幾乎失明，右眼視力模糊，體積較大物件也只能看到輪廓。她需戴眼鏡，但有時「戴嚇除嚇」，案發時剛好忘記戴上。案發當日早上7時多上班，「好多嘢要執」，又要趕在營業前清潔好，感時間緊迫。她打算將垃圾膠袋固定在紙皮盒上，但在收銀台找不到膠紙座，在櫃枱下找到一卷白色東西，以為是膠紙，遂放入褲袋，騰出雙手工作。李稱後來要執拾大量紙皮箱，沒理會褲袋的「膠紙」。<br />\n<br />\n李接著又要趕往下一份兼職，至晚上11時多才回家洗澡，發現褲袋有一卷印花。當時已近深夜，她不知所措，翌朝一早到分店等候開門，店門一開她已將印花放回原位。其後她正要下班時，保安員趙愛虹即截停她並搜袋，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">然後報警</span></strong>。趙向警方稱在手袋搜出一卷印花及10個零散印花，辯方後來要求取得案發翌朝的閉路電視，證實拍下李將印花放回原位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180118/20277861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F20277861&d=hZ%2Fq%2Fd2VlDcwjyJMHBVxpgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=1cac3810\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F20277861&h=16d40832\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180118/20277861</a><br />\n<br />\n費事又有人晌度話唔見印花報警係程序萬寧都冇辦法."},{"pid":"947838251e446c547ecab1f4cffea394b6007ff8","tid":532597,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfeadaa85c3253dc018d91e5367778e43fbb1cb","tid":532597,"uid":121610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:06:25.000Z","msg":"推到個保安仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc28275f1ac6ccc55897ae9c5e8f1e8ff113fdd5","tid":532597,"uid":66870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"推一推先啦"},{"pid":"ab23c4de1e9fe0b9b4736fa652ede4279ef65f2f","tid":532597,"uid":76681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"呢間閪野, 就算佢出來還呀婆清白, 都仍然係仆街來"},{"pid":"81bf9038eebcf12a3798c270b383ac3238f490dd","tid":532597,"uid":2660,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"趙愛虹落假口供係事實 <br />\n點解冇人告佢先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔見印花仲要第二日呀婆收工先報警<br />\n你話唔係想借呢件事炒呀婆我唔信喇<br />\n<br />\n正常做法 一唔見就會立即報警 通知全世界卷印花報廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲點會可以等到呀婆收工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73d70af83fa284dd3468d8f262be6813c855e6e","tid":532597,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"未上熱門 推下"},{"pid":"792d2216b4f432def2a600cbf884398d455362a2","tid":532597,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab23c4de1e9fe0b9b4736fa652ede4279ef65f2f","tid":532597,"uid":76681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"呢間閪野, 就算佢出來還呀婆清白, 都仍然係仆街來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:45:49.000Z","msg":"佢出黎話呀婆係清白<br />\n姐係之前落假口供 <br />\n拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6857d7164f44999e722425d8f3770333b940c69c","tid":532597,"uid":35598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"踩上去洗版還洗版<br />\n好心就睇下自己po啲乜先<br />\n成班親愛的萬寧都唔知做乜鳩"},{"pid":"aa4a27cfd649f37eae70abb8585920270a6dcec2","tid":532597,"uid":140979,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"親愛的萬寧：<br />\n<br />\n失明清潔婆婆像律政司司長鄭若驊般忙碌，好明顯她對印花的警覺性及政治敏感有改善空間，一直沒有留意將印花帶當膠紙帶左返屋企，希望諒解，並代她深表歉意。她已授權認可人士提交補救方案，撥亂反正，印花翌日亦開舖時候已經帶回公司，希望給她空間處理。經過今次印花件，她已汲取教訓（知道印花原來係好X貴），按照律政司違法僭建例子，法律不外乎人情，請不要咄咄逼人，而且相煎何太急，深信定能獲網開一面。<br />\n<br />\n忙於杯葛萬寧的客人 示<br />\n<br />\n班弱智copy呢篇文做乜撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 篇文好撚明顯係將萬寧個責任轉嫁左去個婆婆到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想淡化件事，屌你老母"},{"pid":"bfe07e8488e4048d60f7e62ef25566b059c371da","tid":532597,"uid":82587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27ca1800094f3916f199e61b8cc730c0ab4ac425","tid":532597,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"第二間公司主管出埋黎幫佢做人格擔保 萬寧今次食蕉喇"},{"pid":"45e4f8eb1189bcdd802e4d8b7bad70c9de77c6a3","tid":532597,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b8a4dcf0b132293cb309d0856924c96099476c","tid":532597,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"推。"}]}